    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="lead-big">Strike Action by UCU</span></p>
<p>The University and College Union (UCU) has recently balloted its members for a period of a strike action and that UCU has notified the University that it is calling on its members to take industrial action. This will consist of three days of strike action during November 2022.</p>
<p>This strike action is in response to the new JNCHES 22/23 pay award which was implemented as part of a national bargaining arrangement that determines pay across most of the UK university sector. </p>
<p>As well as the strike action, UCU will also begin action in the form of Action Short of a Strike (ASOS) from 23<sup>rd</sup> of November 2022 until further notice.</p>]]></Value>
